		<description>与动脉相连的精密装置，能够自行提炼植入者的血液产出精血，为防止植入者意外失血而亡还会为其定期注射凝血剂。</description>
		<descriptionHyperlinks>
			<ThingDef>NY_BloodExtracter</ThingDef>
		</descriptionHyperlinks>
		<spawnThingOnRemoved>NY_BloodExtracter</spawnThingOnRemoved>
